{// ningbo mahjong

//✅ riichi tiles + 8 flowers
//✅ 16 rounds
//✅ 14 tile dead wall
// same joker rules as tianjin (flip a dora indicator but it's actually a joker indicator, and the indicator is also a joker, so 7 jokers). a flower indicator indicates all flower tiles as jokers
// joker is called baida
// can use baida to call and to win
//✅ declare flowers before play. must declare drawn flowers later; can't hold onto them or discard them.
// ankan is concealed -- no one can see it until the end of the round

// win con

//✅ 4 sets and a pair
// 4 tai minimum

// yaku (using riichi names out of laziness)

// edge/closed/single wait: 1 tai
// tsumo: 1 tai
// won on baida: 1 tai
// hell wait: 1 tai
// all triplets: 2 tai
// no baida: 1 tai
// chankan: 0 tai
// tenhou/chiihou: 10 tai
// all flowers: 10 tai
// chinitsu: 4 tai
// honitsu: 2 tai
// tsuuiisou: 10 tai
// haitei/houtei: 1 tai
// yakuhai: 1 tai (same as riichi except there's no round wind)
// rinshan: x2
// chankan: x5
// 3 meld penalty: x5 ???

// Some updates here:
// -Chows/Chis are not allowed
// -Updated scoring formula: Total Payout = Tai/Points x Multipliers for Special Situations (Rinshan or Pao)
// -Updated all scoring hands, tenhou 8->10, chihou 10, all 8 flowers 10, tsuuiisou 4->10
// -Rinshin Additional x2, Chankan x5, 3 Meld Penalty x5
// -No dealer bonus
// -Tai to Points 1 to 1
// -Non-discarders do not pay for Ron

  
